{"tid":762442,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人已經覺得自己會成世都係單身","createTime":"2018-07-31T09:38:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-01T11:19:39.000Z","uid":73994,"like":89,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"a26e44721fd818cbb1f83529538fbae7cda93d7e","tid":762442,"uid":73994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T09:38:02.000Z","msg":"已經認清楚自己只係一個平庸平凡既人<br />\n畢竟自己學歷唔高 家境唔好  樣同身高都無<br />\n<br />\n好啦你地可能會話 啱嫁啦 唔好拍拖唔好結婚生仔<br />\n驚累左下一代<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過點都有一份憧憬<br />\n但往往都要向現實低頭<br />\n就係因為太平凡  異性對你唔會有無任何感覺 只會永遠當你係好人一個<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一諗到自己搵唔到比到人鐘意嘅理由<br />\n負能量就出哂黎<br />\n可能結果係注定單身  <br />\n但而家真係好唔想接受<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9504aa82450a96950210794b2153319d8d551332","tid":762442,"uid":34884,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T09:59:18.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"fdaed963083619a84cf783a411b406992fe77b95","tid":762442,"uid":5438,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T12:16:58.000Z","msg":"無自信<br />\n無錢無才華無父幹<br />\n有時真係唔知啲mk仔點解咁好自信<br />\n<br />\n就因為咁唔想主動去識人<br />\n廢事害人害己啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f5489f238e80cef6e847b5f015938ee8b2adb0d","tid":762442,"uid":115510,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T12:17:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f14609bf8f815c0ec5126d655413c2da5463278","tid":762442,"uid":38172,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T12:38:30.000Z","msg":"我相信更多人係已經 經歷過好重既情傷<br />\n<br />\n已經無能力愛另一個人<br />\n<br />\n所以打算一世單身 無謂害人"},{"pid":"ae6a2ecf322a2f78d79fa9c488f29701a9b6e8e8","tid":762442,"uid":36435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T13:32:57.000Z","msg":"唔識同女仔溝通又怕羞"},{"pid":"9afcac4a34f768490e6f872e9553eadb1bc3d2a5","tid":762442,"uid":81437,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-31T13:52